.---------------------.----------------------------------------------------------------.
| WBPerplexity v1.6 : | WBPerplexity is a Workbench puzzle game in which you have to   
`--------------------' rearrange a picture or animation which has been split into a   |
                       certain amount of sections.  To play WBPerplexity, slide the   |
                    |   tiles around  by moving them into the gap in order  to solve   |
                    |   the picture.  WBPerplexity is ideal if your  bored or whilst   |
                    |   waiting for something to download or process.                  |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |   Additional puzzle sets for WBPerplexity  can be found on the   |
                    |   engine nine design web site @ http://www.engine9design.co.uk   |
                    |   and  from Aminet.  Most puzzle sets are in standard IFF ILBM   |
                    |   format, however some may be in either PNG, JFIF/JPGEG or GIF   |
                    |   format, in which case you will require additional data types   |
                    |   to be installed on your system in order play them.             |
                    `------------------------------------------------------------------'

.---------------------.----------------------------------------------------------------.
| fEATURES          : |  WBPerplexity features many funky groovy stuff including the   |
`--------------------'  following :-                                                  |
                                                                                      |
                    |    >< Three modes of play (3x3, 4x4 & 5x5 grid modes             |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< Datatype support                                           |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< Image scaling                                              |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< Animated puzzles                        (Swell!)           |
                    |                                             /                    |
                    |    >< Sounds                           __/\__                    |
                    |                                        \ . /                    |
                    |    >< App Icon & Window                /   \                    |
                    |                                        \/                    |
                    |    >< Save & Load your game                                      |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< Tooltypes                                                  |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< Locale language support                                    |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< Help function                                              |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< On screen move counter and timer                           |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< New Icons and MagicWB support                              |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< Puzzle hotlist in the menu                                 |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< Font sensitive                                             |
                    `------------------------------------------------------------------'

.---------------------.----------------------------------------------------------------.
| iNSTALLATION      : |  To install  WBPerplexity, double  click the  Installer icon   |
`--------------------'  and  follow the  instructions and prompts  provided. If you   |
                        require assistance during the installation, simply click da   |
                    |    "Help..." gadget.                                             |
                    |                                                                  |
        .--.        |    The WBPerplexity installer enables you to install the stuff   |
       (|Oo|)       |    you wish to install, however we strongly recommend that you   |
        | |        |    select those components that are already checked marked.      |
        TT        |                                                                  |
        `++'        |    Before installing, please ensure that you have an upto-date   |
      .--||--.      |    copy of the  "Installer" program  that should be located in   |
      | _`'_ |      |    you "System:C" directory. The install script has been fully   |
      | |  | |      |    tested on an 1200 running OS3.1 / Installer v43.3.            |
      |_|__|_|      |                                                                  |
      (,)(,)      |    The installer allows you to  install MagicWB or NewIcons. I   |
       T  T T       |    personally prefer  NewIcons as it  looks much nicer (Anyone   |
       |  | |       |    wishing to do a new  MagicWB Icon set for this game is most   |
      _|__|_|_      |    welcome). Cheers.                                             |
     (____|___)     |                                                                  |
                    |    Play16 is now  included in the WBPerplexity archive for ppl   |
                    |    who do  not have a copy already.  It is one of the best CLI   |
                    |    based sound players for the Amiga, so lots of RESPECT to Mr   |
                    |    Thomas Wenzel.                                                |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    I have made every attempt to ensure that the installer will   |
                    |    work with as little  trouble as possible, however if u spot   |
                    |    any bugs in the installer script then please contact me.      |
                    `------------------------------------------------------------------'

.---------------------.----------------------------------------------------------------.
| rEQUiREMENTS      : |  In order to get WBPerplexity to work you will need :-         |
`--------------------'                                                                |
                        >< OS 3.0 or higher                                           |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< One mega bytes of available CHIP memory                    |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< JPEG/JFIF, GIF, PNG & ILBM datatypes                       |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< Play16 pr compatable CLI based sound player                |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    >< NewIcons or MagicWB                                        |
                    |                                                                  |
                    |    ...Also YAM to e-mail meeee                                   |
                    `------------------------------------------------------------------'

